*HELP*==jv_display_commands
*HELLO*==say "Hello $username"
*WHAT*NAME*==say "My name is $trigger"
*THANKS*|*THANK YOU*==say "You're welcome"
*GOODBYE*|*BYE*==say "Goodbye $username"; jv_exit
*FORGET*IT*|CANCEL*==bypass=false; say "Ok"
REPEAT*|DO*AGAIN==jv_repeat_last_command
*TEST*==say "It works!"
*VERSION*==say "I am version $jv_version"
*SAY (*) AND (*)==say "(1) (2)"
